OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOften cloudy with showery
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, some may be on the
OL,7,Fheavy side in the west. A few brighter
OL,8,Fspells too with a few sunny intervals,
OL,9,Fthe best of the dry bright weather
OL,10,Faround the Moray Firth. Quite breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThere will be a mixture of
OL,13,Fclear intervals and showers, these
OL,14,Fmore frequent over the Northwest
OL,15,FHighlands in the evening and early
OL,16,Fnight.
OL,17,
OL,18,CFriday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,19,Fscattered showers, these more frequent
OL,20,Fin the far northwest. Lighter winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
